so, in this we choose the CI/CD platform (jenikins,Github action,Gitlab)
--we trigger the pipeline on:
  -Code push to main branch
  -Pull request creation 
--Pipeline stages:
  1.SAST (Static Analysis)
  2.Dependency Vulnerebility Scan
  3.DAST (Dynamic Analysis)
  4.Compilence check
  5.Report generation
  6.Deployment only if all checks pass

so this are stages we follow 

